info.description:
===============
 OpenplansBoot
===============

Obsolete - please use opencore-fassembler_boot instead!
=======================================================

This was a "bootstrap" package used to generate new deployments
of the OpenCore software stack, the web-based group collaboration
toolkit that powers `coactivate.org <http://www.coactivate.org/>`_ and
other websites.

It has been replaced by `opencore-fassembler_boot <http://pypi.python.org/pypi/opencore-fassembler_boot/>`_.
For more detail, please see `Getting Started with OpenCore
<http://www.openplans.org/projects/opencore/getting-started>`_.
